WEBVTT

0
00:00:00.009 --> 00:00:02.470
The Service Operations Workspace homepage

1
00:00:02.630 --> 00:00:05.530
gives you a live role-based overview of your work,

2
00:00:05.760 --> 00:00:09.449
helping you quickly understand what needs attention and take action.

3
00:00:10.810 --> 00:00:13.020
The home page is made up of two main areas.

4
00:00:13.640 --> 00:00:14.439
In the center,

5
00:00:14.560 --> 00:00:17.299
you'll see dashboards that summarize your operational work.

6
00:00:18.120 --> 00:00:21.670
On the right hand side you'll find panels for Announcements,

7
00:00:21.969 --> 00:00:23.059
Upcoming items,

8
00:00:23.209 --> 00:00:24.149
and Quick links.

9
00:00:26.389 --> 00:00:26.950
By default,

10
00:00:27.069 --> 00:00:29.290
the Overview dashboard is selected.

11
00:00:29.549 --> 00:00:32.168
This view focuses on day to day operational work

12
00:00:32.348 --> 00:00:34.139
and highlights what needs your attention.

13
00:00:35.659 --> 00:00:38.459
You can switch between Your Work and Your Team's Work.

14
00:00:39.599 --> 00:00:42.220
Your Work shows records assigned directly to you,

15
00:00:42.560 --> 00:00:45.299
while Your Team's Work shows records assigned to the group

16
00:00:45.439 --> 00:00:47.299
or groups you belong to.

17
00:00:48.580 --> 00:00:52.119
Dashboards in Service Operations Workspace aren't just visual.

18
00:00:52.380 --> 00:00:55.319
You can interact with them to drill into the underlying records.

19
00:00:55.549 --> 00:00:56.720
Selecting a chart

20
00:00:57.060 --> 00:00:58.799
or an individual data point

21
00:00:58.979 --> 00:01:01.400
automatically opens a filtered list below

22
00:01:01.599 --> 00:01:03.439
showing the records that make up that data.

23
00:01:04.828 --> 00:01:08.509
You can also switch between different dashboards using the dashboard selector.

24
00:01:08.738 --> 00:01:10.069
In addition to the Overview,

25
00:01:10.149 --> 00:01:11.848
the IT Agent Dashboard

26
00:01:12.109 --> 00:01:14.208
provides a different perspective on your work.

27
00:01:14.469 --> 00:01:19.049
The IT Agent Dashboard is designed to help you review workload and trends over time.

28
00:01:20.059 --> 00:01:22.400
You can switch between your own metrics

29
00:01:22.580 --> 00:01:24.000
and your team's metrics.

30
00:01:27.819 --> 00:01:30.339
You can also adjust the time period being shown.

31
00:01:36.330 --> 00:01:39.610
The right-hand side of the home page provides supporting information.

32
00:01:40.510 --> 00:01:44.709
Announcements highlight important updates such as outages or major incidents.

33
00:01:45.730 --> 00:01:49.349
The Upcoming panel draws attention to time sensitive items.

35
00:01:51.180 --> 00:01:55.139
Quick Links allow you to add your own frequently used links for easy access.

36
00:01:55.379 --> 00:01:56.720
These links are personal

37
00:01:56.860 --> 00:02:00.790
and help you tailor the workspace to the tools and resources you use most.
